collection of my vim configuration options and plugins in OpenSuSe

Move the vimrc.local in /etc

Add the follow ine at the end of /etc/vimrc file
if filereadable("/etc/vimrc.local")
  exec "source /etc/vimrc.local"
endif

Move folders to $HOME/.vim folder.
e.g.
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/doc
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/ftplugin
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/nerdtree_plugin
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/plugin
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/syntax
.....
